modName: Argonian Assemblage Bed of Setvi - Skyrim
summary: This mod will only add one bed at the Argonian Assemblage at Windhelm's docks for (Argonian) roleplay and immersion purpose. Just a small mod done for personal use but I want to share it with you. Maybe it can help. Thanks for support, enjoy, Setvi.
